  <summary date="2015-03-04T05:00:00Z" status="Introduced in House">Child Tax Credit Permanency Act of 2015 

This bill amends the Internal Revenue Code, with respect to the child tax credit, to: (1) adjust the earned income threshold for determining the amount of the refundable portion of such credit, and (2) provide for an inflation adjustment to the $1,000 credit amount for calendar years after 2013.</summary>
